'''丹皮酚'''（{{lang|en|paeonol}}）是在[[芍药属|芍药属]]<ref>Zhang, L., Li, D. C., & Liu, L. F. (2019). Paeonol: pharmacological effects and mechanisms of action. International immunopharmacology, 72, 413-421. {{PMID|31030097}}  {{Doi|10.1016/j.intimp.2019.04.033}}</ref>植物（如牡丹）、 <ref name="Fukuhara">{{Cite journal|title=Paeonol: a bio-antimutagen isolated from a crude drug, moutan cortex|journal=Agricultural and Biological Chemistry|issue=5|doi=10.1271/bbb1961.51.1441|year=1987|volume=51|pages=1441–1442|id={{INIST|7609719}}|lastauthoramp=yes|subscription=free}}</ref>[[一把伞南星|一把伞南星]]， <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Isolation of paeonol from Arisaema erubescens|journal=Planta Medica|issue=6|doi=10.1055/s-2006-959390|year=1995|volume=61|pages=586–587|pmid=8824957|id={{INIST|2920867}}|lastauthoramp=yes}}</ref>和[[日本薯蓣|日本薯蓣]]中发现的一种酚类化合物。<ref name="Miyazama">{{Cite journal|title=Antimutagenic Activity of (+)-β-Eudesmol and Paeonol fromDioscorea japonica|last=Miyazawa|first=Mitsuo|last2=Shimamura|first2=Hideo|journal=Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry|issue=7|doi=10.1021/jf950792u|year=1996|volume=44|pages=1647–1650|last3=Nakamura|first3=Sei-Ichi|last4=Kameoka|first4=Hiromu}}</ref>它是某些[[中医学|中药]]中的成分。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Development of microwave-assisted extraction followed by headspace single-drop microextraction for fast determination of paeonol in traditional Chinese medicines|last=Deng|first=Chunhui|last2=Yao|first2=Ning|journal=Journal of Chromatography A|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.chroma.2005.11.023|year=2006|volume=1103|pages=15–21|pmid=16309693|last3=Wang|first3=Ben|last4=Zhang|first4=Xiangmin}}</ref> 

== 生物学作用 ==
已经观察到丹皮酚在体外或[[动物模型|动物模型]]中的许多生物学作用。丹皮酚可提高[[阿茲海默症|阿尔茨海默病]]大鼠模型的皮质[[细胞色素c氧化酶|细胞色素氧化酶]]和血管[[肌动蛋白|肌动蛋白]]水平，并改善其行为。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Paeonol increases levels of cortical cytochrome oxidase and vascular actin and improves behavior in a rat model of Alzheimer's disease|url=https://cloudfront.escholarship.org/dist/prd/content/qt1qs126j6/qt1qs126j6.pdf|last=Zhou|first=Jun|last2=Zhou|first2=Li|journal=Brain Research|doi=10.1016/j.brainres.2011.02.064|year=2011|volume=1388|pages=141–7|pmid=21377451|last3=Hou|first3=Deren|last4=Tang|first4=Jiaochun|last5=Sun|first5=Juanjuan|last6=Bondy|first6=Stephen C.|access-date=2020-07-17|archive-date=2018-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724164434/https://cloudfront.escholarship.org/dist/prd/content/qt1qs126j6/qt1qs126j6.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

丹皮酚具有[[抑制基因突變|抗突变]]活性。 <ref name="Fukuhara">{{Cite journal|title=Paeonol: a bio-antimutagen isolated from a crude drug, moutan cortex|journal=Agricultural and Biological Chemistry|issue=5|doi=10.1271/bbb1961.51.1441|year=1987|volume=51|pages=1441–1442|id={{INIST|7609719}}|lastauthoramp=yes|subscription=free}}</ref><ref name="Miyazama">{{Cite journal|title=Antimutagenic Activity of (+)-β-Eudesmol and Paeonol fromDioscorea japonica|last=Miyazawa|first=Mitsuo|last2=Shimamura|first2=Hideo|journal=Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry|issue=7|doi=10.1021/jf950792u|year=1996|volume=44|pages=1647–1650|last3=Nakamura|first3=Sei-Ichi|last4=Kameoka|first4=Hiromu}}</ref> 它还在[[卡拉胶|卡拉胶]]引起的痛觉过敏中具有[[抗炎性|抗炎]]和[[镇痛药|镇痛]]作用。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Anti-inflammatory and analgesic effects of paeonol in carrageenan-evoked thermal hyperalgesia|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-of-pharmacology_2003-07_139_6/page/1146|last=Chou|first=Tz-Chong|journal=British Journal of Pharmacology|issue=6|doi=10.1038/sj.bjp.0705360|year=2003|volume=139|pages=1146–52|pmc=1573952|pmid=12871833}}</ref>丹皮酚可通过调节[[組織胺|组胺]]和[[肿瘤坏死因子-α|TNF-α]]抑制[[過敏性休克|过敏反应]] 。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Paeonol inhibits anaphylactic reaction by regulating histamine and TNF-α|last=Kim|first=Sung Hoon|last2=Kim|first2=Seung-Ae|journal=International Immunopharmacology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.intimp.2003.12.013|year=2004|volume=4|pages=279–87|pmid=14996419|last3=Park|first3=Mi-Kyung|last4=Kim|first4=Seung-Hyung|last5=Park|first5=Young-Doo|last6=Na|first6=Ho-Jeong|last7=Kim|first7=Hyung-Min|last8=Shin|first8=Min-Kyu|last9=Ahn|first9=Kyoo-Seok}}</ref> 

== 金属配合物 ==
丹皮酚的金属配合物分别在不存在和存在吡啶溶剂的情况下表现出四面体和八面体的几何配形。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Solvent effect on neutral Co (II) complexes of paeonol derivative equalitative and quantitative studies from energy frame work and Hirshfeld surface analysis|last=Patel|first=Mahesh kumar|journal=Journal of Molecular Structure|doi=10.1016/j.molstruc.2019.06.050|year=2019|volume=1196|page=119–131|bibcode=2019JMoSt1196..119P}}</ref> 

